          <span class="MB_SubHead"><a name="336"></a>UI Information</span> 
          
          <br>
          Submitted by <a href="mailto:bodi@monkly-business.com">Bodi</a> on 8/1/2002 3:57:39 AM</p>
        <ul>
          <p class="MB_Body"><p>Seems I did not make it clear with regards to the UI links in the New Features forum. Please post links to UI sites, or links to DOWNLOADS of your mods (including images so people know what they look like) in <a href="http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm16.showMessage?topicID=132.topic"> >>this<< </a> thread, and SCREENSHOTS of your current setup where you are not giving any linked information, <a href="http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm16.showMessage?topicID=150.topic"> >>here<< </a>.

